  <header class="main-hd">
    <h3 class="title">
      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/5453540/" class="title-link">《罗马帝国衰亡史》读了一半有感…</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-5453540"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/hanslu/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img1.doubanio.com/icon/u4430634-7.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/hanslu/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">陆大鹏Hans</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar50 main-title-rating" title="力荐"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2012-06-04"
      class="main-meta">2012-06-04 15:47:04</span>
</div>

  </header>

        <div class="main-bd">
          <div id="review_5453540_short" class="review-short">
            <div class="short-content">
                  《罗马帝国衰亡史》读了一半有感…  前前后后花了近一年功夫，把吉本的这部堂皇巨著读了一半，也就是到了西罗马帝国覆灭的时节。 以前不知道吉本的谋篇布局，原以为既然叫罗马帝国衰亡史，肯定是到阿拉里克和阿提拉就结束了，毕竟我向来并不认为拜占庭和神罗是罗马帝国。现在看...

                    <a class="pl" href="https://book.douban.com/review/5453540/#comments">(8回应)</a>
                  <div class="more-info pl clearfix">
                    <span class="left">19有用 / 5没用</span>
                        <span class="publisher left">
                            London: Methuen, currently reprinted (New York: AMS Press, 1974)1909版</span>
                  </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div id="review_5453540_full" class="hidden">
            <div id="review_5453540_full_content" class="full-content"></div>
          </div>
        </div>
    </div>
